# ngx_http_heavybag_module - Cookie header signature blocklist
#
# Format: one PCRE2 pattern per line, optional trailing action token.
#   <pattern>[ <action>]      action in { 404 (default), 403, 444 }
#
# Patterns are matched case-insensitively against each %-decoded Cookie
# request header value (a client may send several). Patterns sharing an
# action compile into one alternation regex; this file is hot-reloadable.

# ---- scanner / tool fingerprints in cookies --------------------------------
sqlmap               404
acunetix             403

# ---- obvious injection attempts in cookie values ---------------------------
<script              444
